24:43.082 --> 24:44.482
This is hilarious.

24:44.484 --> 24:45.616
I just said to Tom,

24:45.618 --> 24:48.252
you know, "Will you join me on
the ticket as my running mate?"

24:48.254 --> 24:50.120
Okay, so then tell
what you just did.

24:50.122 --> 24:51.956
- Again?
