24:51.958 --> 24:53.858
- Please. Can't wait.
- It's hilarious. Tell him.

24:53.860 --> 24:57.194
Well, I said, "Madam President,
with deep regret..."

24:57.196 --> 24:59.063
No, you didn't say that.
