( laughing )

25:08.841 --> 25:13.010
He accepted.
Oh, it's tremendous.

25:13.779 --> 25:15.279
Welcome to the ticket.

25:15.281 --> 25:17.548
- Thank you, Mike.
- You joker.

25:17.550 --> 25:19.216
